============================================================
测试：_resolve_recovery_target
============================================================

场景：无请求凭证名称 - 自动分配
输入：handle='alice', requested_credential_name=None, replace_existing=False
输出：credential_name='alice', old_credential=None

场景：请求新凭证名称
输入：handle='bob', requested_credential_name='bob_new', replace_existing=False
输出：credential_name='bob_new', old_credential=None

场景：请求现有凭证但不替换
输入：handle='charlie', requested_credential_name='existing_cred', replace_existing=False
输出：预期错误但未发生

场景：请求现有凭证并替换
输入：handle='david', requested_credential_name='replace_cred', replace_existing=True
输出：credential_name='replace_cred', old_credential=None

